    I'm so glad you found my site and that you're interested in writing about your life.<br><br>I'm excited to get to know you, whether you're already writing about your life and trying to get better at it or you're just getting started.<br><br>My goal is to get more twenty-something women to write about their lives because I believe the world needs women to tell it like it is. I have also experienced the effects of keeping secrets first hand, and trust me - it's toxic<br><br> I want to support women so they can get their stories out into the world where they belong.
  </p>
<span class=break><h2>“The role of a writer is not to say what we can all say, but what we are unable to say.”<br><br>― Anaïs Nin</h2></span>
  </p>
